{"tid":2448280,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"希望特首林鄭月娥可以將警察家庭列為第一個全體接種疫苗組別","createTime":"2021-03-15T22:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T01:47:44.000Z","uid":32051,"like":102,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae65ab68caf7f8b5c03eda0052f582a04e5409a","tid":2448280,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T22:20:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580746-20210315.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580746-20210315.htm&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=40144602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580746-20210315.htm&h=f094a9c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580746-20210315.htm</a><br />\n38歲男督察初步確診　部分警務及文職人員須檢測<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，一名駐守刑事部的38歲男督察初步確診新型肺炎。他最後一日上班日為上周五。他的家人較早前懷疑曾接觸確診個案，他接受測試，今日病毒測試呈陽性反應。他於過去14日沒有外遊記錄，工作期間有佩戴口罩，並沒有與公眾接觸。<br />\n<br />\n警方又指，在等候衞生署進一步評估及建議前，與該名督察可能有緊密接觸的警務及文職人員，獲安排接受病毒檢測。警方會派員清潔及消毒該名督察的相關工作地方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">我真係好擔心前線警員面對嘅壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n希望佢哋全家齊齊整整，齊齊有疫苗打。<br />\n警員可以免後顧之憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"23d8bbf6bb0744f9f33808e9cae9fce2da8935b9","tid":2448280,"uid":32051,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T22:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYCZU3V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYCZU3V.png&h=667d2595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一like一支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望特首睇到"},{"pid":"a7bfa61a5f95f4bdf978a78ad758eb7e33d20fff","tid":2448280,"uid":32051,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T23:18:15.000Z","msg":"支持國家，支持科興。<br />\n<br />\n港警作表率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推動疫苗接種比率"},{"pid":"06e248a5522a4ee8c7c79d5dc85e995a6ab311a5","tid":2448280,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T23:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開心上路"},{"pid":"5e12d819fa0ead063801c76e770367e57d41f01a","tid":2448280,"uid":32051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06e248a5522a4ee8c7c79d5dc85e995a6ab311a5","tid":2448280,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T23:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開心上路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T23:35:55.000Z","msg":"安心出行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213c6afbe45757cb5c0cc0aacb26a4ae73273283","tid":2448280,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e12d819fa0ead063801c76e770367e57d41f01a","tid":2448280,"uid":32051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06e248a5522a4ee8c7c79d5dc85e995a6ab311a5","tid":2448280,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T23:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開心上路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T23:35:55.000Z","msg":"安心出行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T23:36:53.000Z","msg":"放心 一打就全家打 服務幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"